{"tid":1143522,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Days Gone 白金最終評價: 7.5分","createTime":"2019-05-07T19:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T11:07:04.000Z","uid":74970,"like":8,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"75e75b261f4b68d55d89afb8a9de68e4b172b62e","tid":1143522,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T19:16:35.000Z","msg":"白己金, 個人會比7.5分左右<br />\n暴走潮好玩, 畫面, 音效, 配音都好好, 故事唔錯, 電單車手感好<br />\n暴走潮需要用場景, 道具, 走位去打上百隻至幾百隻既屍, 好刺激<br />\n當然係遊戲中後期先會玩到, 初期唔夠裝備跟本無得打<br />\n主線流程起碼40粒鐘, 好襟玩, 係就有D內容重複<br />\n但果種重複內容中夾集好多故事同cutscenes,<br />\n同埋個開放世界遠遠未有ubi果種滿圖問號, 高度作業感既問題<br />\n系統樣樣有D, 雖然手感一般, 新意唔多, 有d bugs同技術上既問題<br />\n但patch得都幾快, 而且唔算嚴重隨fallout 76, anthem果種<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔算8分以上佳作, 但遠遠無媒體講到咁差<br />\n特別係ign同gamespot講到得6.5分, 5分"},{"pid":"98e7d246e4be2318bf6c5b7ebc1297c43ffb63e6","tid":1143522,"uid":74970,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T03:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3036193b2919b51eb3ad70648d9b525f05f8820","tid":1143522,"uid":105511,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf645d11a49e7393fa4fdde22005d2618e798c32","tid":1143522,"uid":74970,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"今次ign同gamespot兩個reviewers都好似係女權撚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngamespot果個仲要係網上知名&quot;too much water&quot;review果條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8JrEF9CNOd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8JrEF9CNOd4&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8SywbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=3c972ec4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8JrEF9CNOd4</a>"},{"pid":"f108fb8533efb4d93a45a61c1736f0ddebca2428","tid":1143522,"uid":74970,